OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,FA Reform councillor who was suspended
OL,7,Fover historic social media posts
OL,8,Fwithin days of being elected said he
OL,9,F"likes to make jokes about taboo
OL,10,Ftopics" in his first comments on the
OL,11,Fissue.
OL,13,FNathaniel Menday won a seat to
OL,14,Frepresent Woodhouse ward on Sheffield
OL,15,FCouncil in the 7 May elections.
OL,17,FBut he was then suspended over reports
OL,18,Fhe had previously shared photos on X
OL,19,Fof a swastika and Hitler's Mein Kampf.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
