CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,FIt was also claimed he suggested the
OL,7,FUK has a "subhuman underclass".
OL,9,FReform said he had "brought the party
OL,10,Finto disrepute".
OL,12,FIn a lengthy social media post Mr
OL,13,FMenday said he was "naturally
OL,14,Fconsidering my future" and "would be
OL,15,Fputting some distance between myself
OL,16,Fand this for a few weeks, specifically
OL,17,Fa few thousand miles".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
