FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,FHe said his suspension was the result
OL,7,Fof "gutter journalism" and called for
OL,8,Fa ban on websites which allowed
OL,9,Fdeleted tweets to be recovered.
OL,11,FMr Menday added: "I'm not apologising
OL,12,Ffor tweets that have been deleted,
OL,13,Fbecause ultimately what more can I do?
OL,15,F"Likewise, I'm not apologising for
OL,16,Fjokes or memes... my sense of humour
OL,17,Fisn't for everyone but neither are my
OL,18,Fposts.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,F"When I talk about jokes, memes, or
OL,7,Fposts that were meant as tongue in
OL,8,Fcheek, I'm referring overwhelmingly to
OL,9,Fso-called Nazi related content.
OL,11,F"I like to make jokes about taboo
OL,12,Ftopics as a lot of normal young lads
OL,13,Fdo and there's nothing more subversive
OL,14,Fthan jokes about this, without being
OL,15,Fdirectly hateful at least, which I try
OL,16,Fnot to do.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
