PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,F"The entire western, particularly
OL,7,FEnglish speaking, world is
OL,8,Ffundamentally paranoid about Nazi's
OL,9,F(sic) under the bed, they stifle our
OL,10,Fpublic discourse by labelling anyone
OL,11,Fwith views to the right of (Lib Dem
OL,12,Fleader) Ed Davey as being the second
OL,13,Fcoming of Hitler, and it's so
OL,14,Ftiresome."
OL,16,FHe said he was not a Nazi, but said he
OL,17,Fwas "proudly" right wing and had
OL,18,F"flirted with more radical ways of
OL,19,Fthinking".
OL,26,@sD@\pmtD@Gpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
