PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779296759
OL,3,CSuspended Reform councillor refuses to
OL,4,Capologise over 'Nazi-related content'
OL,6,FBut he aded: "I reject any ideology
OL,7,Fthat would target people simply
OL,8,Fbecause of who they are. I am not
OL,9,Fprejudiced and I think the people who
OL,10,Fknow me know this, I believe in
OL,11,Ftreating people as individuals before
OL,12,Fall else and if I continue as
OL,13,Fcouncillor no matter your background I
OL,14,Fwill do my best for you if you come to
OL,15,Fme."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
